  "formulaSource": "Charger hardware pricing from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 national average surveys and manufacturer MSRP data for ChargePoint, JuiceBox, Wallbox, Tesla, and Grizzl-E units. Charging speed specifications from U.S. Department of Energy Alternative Fuels Data Center (AFDC). Labor rates from Bureau of Labor Statistics OES data for electricians (SOC 47-2111). Circuit distance multipliers from HomeAdvisor contractor survey data. Panel upgrade and permit costs from HomeAdvisor 2025-2026. Regional labor multipliers derived from BLS OES regional wage data.",
